<tr id="L326"><td><a href="#L326">326</a></td><td>TIMICIN:  Do you believe I love you? I do, you know. But finally, if that is my only reason to stay alive.</td></tr>

<tr id="L327"><td><a href="#L327">327</a></td><td>LWAXANA:  It's not enough.</td></tr>

<tr id="L328"><td><a href="#L328">328</a></td><td>TIMICIN:  Almost. Almost but not quite. I can't be that selfish, Lwaxana. I am not the person to lead the revolt.</td></tr>

