<tr id="L329"><td><a href="#L329">329</a></td><td>TIMICIN:  I do apologise for all the turmoil I've created.</td></tr>

<tr id="L330"><td><a href="#L330">330</a></td><td>PICARD:  Doctor, I would deeply regret it if you were returning only to ease diplomatic tensions.</td></tr>

<tr id="L331"><td><a href="#L331">331</a></td><td>TIMICIN:  It is more. Much more.</td></tr>

